  "detailed_description": "Hi I am Rainn...Game writer and developer<br>Thanks for being here, please note that you don't need to read Episode 0 before this one as the actual story starts here.<br>you can still check out Episode 0 when you finish the whole novel<br><br>please check out the demo on itch.io and share your opinion with me DEMO<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>The eight students of the elite class find themselves going up against a mysterious masked individual with unclear, and potentially dangerous motives. <br><br>Be careful not to lose!<br><br><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An exciting and fast-paced story<br></li><li>Cool new graphics<br></li><li>We have redrawn all the characters with many costumes and expressions<br></li><li>More than 40 backgrounds and 18 CGs<br></li><li>Expressive music<br></li><li>steam achievements<br></li><li>A gallery for viewing unlocked CGs</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Hi I am Rainn...Game writer and developer<br>Thanks for being here, please note that you don't need to read Episode 0 before this one as the actual story starts here.<br>you can still check out Episode 0 when you finish the whole novel<br><br>please check out the demo on itch.io and share your opinion with me DEMO<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>The eight students of the elite class find themselves going up against a mysterious masked individual with unclear, and potentially dangerous motives. <br><br>Be careful not to lose!<br><br><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An exciting and fast-paced story<br></li><li>Cool new graphics<br></li><li>We have redrawn all the characters with many costumes and expressions<br></li><li>More than 40 backgrounds and 18 CGs<br></li><li>Expressive music<br></li><li>steam achievements<br></li><li>A gallery for viewing unlocked CGs</li></ul>",
